        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gp-600 dark:bg-neon-sky"></div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:gradient-text transition-all leading-snug">原点を振り返る―LayerX福島良典×Goodpatch土屋尚史が語る10年の歩みとデザインの価値</p>
